<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<assessmentItem
        xmlns="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqti_v2p1"
        xmlns:pci="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/portableCustomInteraction_v1"
        xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance"
        xsi:schemaLocation="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqti_v2p1 http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqti_v2p1.xsd"
        identifier="fractions-no-dependencies"
        title="Simple Shaded Grid Interaction with no module dependencies"
        adaptive="false"
        timeDependent="false">
    <responseDeclaration identifier="RESPONSE" cardinality="single" baseType="integer">
        <correctResponse>
            <value>1</value>
        </correctResponse>
    </responseDeclaration>
    <responseDeclaration identifier="EXAMPLE" cardinality="single" baseType="integer">
        <correctResponse>
            <value>6</value>
        </correctResponse>
    </responseDeclaration>
    <outcomeDeclaration identifier="SCORE" cardinality="single" baseType="float">
        <defaultValue>
            <value>0.0</value>
        </defaultValue>
    </outcomeDeclaration>
    <itemBody>
        <div>
            Mary is saving to buy a birthday present for her mother.
            Every week she counts the money she has saved into piles of $5.
            At the end of the first week Mary had saved $10 and was planning to
            buy her mother a present worth $30.
            <p> </p>
            She represented this in the following shaded chart with a shaded square
            for every $5 saved and a target of $30.
            <p> </p>
            <customInteraction responseIdentifier="EXAMPLE" id="shadedGridExample">
                <portableCustomInteraction customInteractionTypeIdentifier="hmhcoPciShading" xmlns="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/portableCustomInteraction_v1">
                    <properties>
                        <property key="controls">none</property>
                        <property key="render">grid</property>
                        <property key="selected">0.0,1.0</property>
                        <property key="selected_color">red</property>
                        <property key="unselected_color">white</property>
                        <property key="dimension1_initial">3</property>
                        <property key="dimension2_initial">2</property>
                        <property key="element_diameter">60</property>
                        <property key="value">numShaded</property>
                        <property key="active">0</property>
                    </properties>
                    <modules>
                        <!-- the primaryPath URL is deliberately incorrect to demonstrate the use of the fallbackPath -->
                        <module id="shading" primaryPath="hmh/modules/shading.js"/>
                    </modules>
                    <markup xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">
                        <!-- PCI hook dynamically adds content to this div. -->
                        <div></div>
                    </markup>
                </portableCustomInteraction>
            </customInteraction>
            <p>By the second week she has already saved the exact amount she planned
                on spending on the present ($30) and is trying to work out if she will be able
                to afford a more expensive present costing $45.</p>
            <p>To help her do this use the buttons below to create a chart representing
                $45 assuming that each square represents $5 and then click to shade the
                fraction of the chart representing the amount saved in two weeks.</p>
            <customInteraction responseIdentifier="RESPONSE" id="shadedGridPresent">
                <portableCustomInteraction customInteractionTypeIdentifier="hmhcoPciShading" xmlns="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/portableCustomInteraction_v1">
                    <properties>
                        <property key="controls">full</property>
                        <property key="render">grid</property>
                        <property key="selected_color">red</property>
                        <property key="unselected_color">white</property>
                        <property key="dimension1_initial">2</property>
                        <property key="dimension2_initial">2</property>
                        <property key="element_diameter">60</property>
                        <property key="value">numShaded</property>
                    </properties>
                    <modules>
                        <!-- the primaryPath URL is deliberately incorrect to demonstrate the use of the fallbackPath -->
                        <module id="shading" primaryPath="hmh/modules/shading.js"/>
                    </modules>
                    <markup xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">
                        <!-- PCI module dynamically adds content to this div. -->
                        <div></div>
                    </markup>
                </portableCustomInteraction>
            </customInteraction>
        </div>
    </itemBody>
    <responseProcessing template="http://www.imsglobal.org/question/qti_v2p1/rptemplates/match_correct"/>
</assessmentItem>